{"tid":609672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中銀熄機】周六晚起停運16小時 客戶呻麻煩要㩒定錢先","createTime":"2018-03-29T08:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T08:33:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8ea743f74c762fc7c74e66130889cf2e36d8a6","tid":609672,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"中銀香港將於後晚(31/3)起「熄機16小時」，今天是熄機前最後到分行打簿的機會。停運期間，中銀將大規模提升系統，全線不論境內外的自動櫃員機（ATM）、網上銀行、手機銀行等將暫停，亦不可持中銀提款卡到其他銀通成員銀行ATM提款。43歲的凌小姐直言並不知道此事，平常也會使用ATM服務，她覺得停機很麻煩，「咁我咪2號先㩒錢囉，依家會攞定啲錢先」，她認為服務上可以再做好一點，「因為無通知我哋啲市民囉」。<br />\n<br />\n72歲的梁伯趁假期前夕用ATM提款，但他也不知道停機的消息，得知後直言「好麻煩，中銀應該搞返好，搞返好就無乜事囉」。54歲的文先生表示，幾日前已得知消息，對他沒有太大的影響，「咁仲有第二間銀行嘅戶口架嘛」，但他也覺得有改善的空間，「依家唔係最好囉，當然佢有佢嘅原因啦，咁假期有好多人要㩒錢消費架嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n55歲的劉先生說，中銀停機對他沒有影響，「我都唔用ATM，無用佢呢個服務，今日係嚟入數」，但他表示，中銀可以再早點通知客戶，「同埋唔好斷哂服務囉」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》沙士15周年系列網站，正式登場：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2F&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c7956ec8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2F&h=1028b085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180329/58009723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180329%2F58009723&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a9585c23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180329%2F58009723&h=444827a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180329/58009723</a>"},{"pid":"5fa5967ac57e8710ac758f8e32242b4c87ddd8b5","tid":609672,"uid":35045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"戇鳩先用中資銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dafc7bcbb5d20218390e9cf86e8473b423395b0","tid":609672,"uid":48276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fa5967ac57e8710ac758f8e32242b4c87ddd8b5","tid":609672,"uid":35045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"戇鳩先用中資銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:33:44.000Z","msg":"公司逼只可以用中資銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}